snippet.title: Airscape The Fall of Gravity - Indie Game Spotlight
snippet.description:
Learn more Airscape The Fall of Gravity at: http://airscapegame.com/

Airscape is a fast-paced platformer set on an alien world during a cataclysmic mechanical invasion. The game's unique gravity system allows for the creation of beautiful, mind-boggling levels that bring fresh challenges to players. An assembly of devious, intelligent obstacles and enemies make the game a difficult, intense, and exciting experience.

If you enjoyed the video, please consider hitting the Like button. It helps a lot
